{"tid":427620,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS] MHP2G@無限loop","createTime":"2017-10-07T14:51:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T11:17:32.000Z","uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d62bdc6e648f870935bf2e760d33fd8aec3548bb","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"無新game 都係同一隻咋。<br />\n呢幾日我係apps台down過試玩過好多隻game<br />\n最尾都搵唔到我想要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊個個又係度玩switch個monhunt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n把心一橫download返呢隻差唔多有10年歷史嘅game<br />\n早幾年都玩過一次架喇<br />\n但無綁定到咁就洗走曬啲資料...<br />\n重新黎過依家卡緊怪鳥一路都打唔到個怪鳥之耳出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開個PO想睇下以前玩過嘅你<br />\n或者玩完switch屎忽痕想試下手機版嘅玩家（雖然都無乜可能）<br />\n如果有興趣 可以join我一齊打下集會所喎<br />\n無論有無人我都應該繼續玩架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef60de0d23a6f13fc090a3a17c19f2aac0b30bd","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"df9c78bef529d597b4fb6ec58976db2e78f5abeb","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:25:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e1c5777047e9f23e0806b8ebba23ad88c3951817","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f35c3a9fa6b991d7cad7d487e4d24ac675ca4c7d","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aedc26e13398edee69eff990d0a9b270b65a2fe","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T01:21:16.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d410008de90e727de7b28bca5b649541edd71e35","tid":427620,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T02:28:00.000Z","msg